* Steve Harvey as Steve (guest star; episode “Jay the Artist”) 
* Damon Wayans Jr. as John (seasons 2–4)
* Liliana Mumy as Rachel McNamara (seasons 2–4)
* Jessica Sara as Melissa (seasons 2–3)
