* Brian Holtzman as Brian (seasons 3–4)
* Todd Lynn as Todd (seasons 3–4)
* Ella Joyce as Jasmine Scott (seasons 4-5)
* Lester Speight as Calvin Scott (seasons 4–5)
* Sean Whalen as Larry (season 4)

